      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not in drivable shape. It requires significant mechanical attention, including a suspected blown head gasket and a transmission that slips badly. The exterior has noticeable rust and several large dents, while the interior shows heavy wear and staining. This car is ideal as a parts vehicle or a major restoration project for a dedicated mechanic.",
