    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This distinguished vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Meticulously maintained and presenting in commendable condition, it offers a seamless blend of performance and sophisticated styling. All mechanical systems have been thoroughly vetted to ensure continued reliability, making this an exceptional acquisition for those who demand both quality and value. Experience the assurance of a well-preserved automobile that is prepared for immediate service.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
